arStrings.szText: Each time you use a Skill with a Resource Cost, gain {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c} increased damage and Resource Cost is increased by {c_number}[Affix_Value_1|%+|]{/c} for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds, stacking up to {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"]{/c} times.
